7 steps for building a website\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl460\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 1. Define your project
\f3\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Start off by defining the goal of your project. This can be showing your portfolio to the world, selling an e-book, building a blog, etc.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Also define your audience. Ask yourself: which is the typical user that will visit my website?\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
This is important, because you should always design with your goal and audience in mind.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl460\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 \cb3 2. Plan out everything
\f3\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Once your project is defined, plan your content carefully. This includes text, images, videos, icons, etc.\cb1 \
\ls2\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
It plays an important role when you start thinking about what you want on your website and what you don't. Defining the content before actually starting the design is called the\'a0
\f4\i content-first approach
\f3\i0 . It means that you should design for the content, instead of designing a webpage and then filling it with some stuff.\cb1 \
\ls2\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Define the navigation.\cb1 \
\ls2\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Define the site structure. You can draw a sitemap in this step if we're talking about a bigger project.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl460\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 \cb3 3. Sketch your ideas before you design
\f3\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Now it's time to get inspired and think about your design.\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Then, get the ideas out of your head. And with that I mean that you should sketch your ideas before you start designing. It will help you explore ideas and create a concept of what you want to build. Using pencil and paper is a great way of quickly retaining your valuable ideas.\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Make as many sketches as you want, but don't spend too much time perfecting anything. Once you have an initial idea, you can concentrate on the details when designing in HTML and CSS.\cb1 \
\ls3\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
I advise you to never, ever start designing without having an idea of what you want to build. Getting inspiration is very important in this phase, and I already told you how to do that!\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl460\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 \cb3 4. Design and develop your website
\f3\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
After sketching, start to design your website using all the guidelines and tips you've learned in the web design section.\cb1 \
\ls4\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
You'll do that using HTML and CSS, which is called\'a0
\f4\i designing in the browser
\f3\i0 . Designing in the browser is basically designing and developing at the same time.\cb1 \
\ls4\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
There are more and more designers leaving traditional design programs such as Photoshop and start designing in the browser. The biggest reason for this is that you can't design responsive websites in photoshop. It also saves you tons of time.\cb1 \
\ls4\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
In this phase, you'll use your sketches, content and planning decisions you've made in steps 1, 2 and 3.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl460\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 \cb3 5. It's not done yet: optimization
\f3\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Before you can actually launch your beautiful masterpiece for the world to see it, we have to optimize its performance in terms of site speed.\cb1 \
\ls5\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
You also need to do some basic search engine optimization (SEO) for search engines such as google.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl460\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 \cb3 6. Launch the masterpiece
\f3\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Your optimized website is now finally ready to launch.\cb1 \
\ls6\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
All you need for launching is a webserver that will host your website and deliver it to the world.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl460\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf2 \cb3 7. Site maintenance
\f3\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl340\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
The launch of your website is not the end of the story.\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Now it's time to monitor your users' behavior and make some changes to your website if necessary.\cb1 \
\ls7\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
You should also update your content regularly in order to show your users that your website is alive! For instance, a blog can be a great way of doing that.\cb1 \
